title: What does "taken for granted" mean? Could you provide an example?

og.title: What does "taken for granted" mean? Could you provide an example?
og.description:
Answer (1 of 49): Taken for granted is when you have something valuable and you do not take explicit actions to nourish, preserve and flourish it.

We are given privileges by our life and those who have ventured in our lives. These privileges may be material, may be love, concern, respect or abst...
